question: Will Tiktok be banned in the US by May 31?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if the TikTok app is removed/unavailable to download from both the Apple app store and Google Play store in the United States by May 31, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

The primary resolution source for this market will be information from Apple and the US Apple App Store, and Alphabet/Google and Google Play, however a consensus of credible reporting will also be used.

question: $ARB above $2 one week after launch?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if Arbitrum token's price is above $2.0000 (i.e. $2.0001 or greater) one week after launch. Otherwise, the market will resolve to "No."

"one week after launch" is defined as exactly 7 days (168 hours) after the token was claimable.

The resolution source for this market will be consensus of highly liquid price sources as to whether Arbitrum's token is above $2 one week after launch.
